Interface CouponDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CouponDBDAO

    public interface CouponDAO
    All the methods relevant to coupon bean. These methods will be overwritten to allow interface with the relevant Database/file. In this case we are interfacing with Derby DB.
